# Sadovy, Timiryazevskoye Rural Settlement, Maykopsky District, Republic of Adygea

}}
Sadovy () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Timiryazevskoye Rural Settlement of Maykopsky District, Russia. The population was 160 in 2018. There is one street.
Geography
Sadovy is located  southwest of Tulsky (the district's administrative centre) by road. Shuntuk is the nearest rural locality.
